Introducing VNTG 7.0 your all in one vintage services hub offering a range of features to bring nostalgic charm to your memories. Studio: Import and transform your photos into vintage masterpieces with ease. Rediscover the beauty of bygone eras using our filters effects and editing tools. Prints: Order high quality vintage prints of your favorite photos and have them delivered to your doorstep. Preserve cherished moments in tangible form. New Features Unveiled in VNTG 7.0: Introducing the sleek and refreshed logo for VNTG embodying a new era of style and innovation. Experience the allure of an exquisite brand new user interface design that elevates your interaction to unprecedented levels of elegance and functionality. Effortlessly import and utilize your cherished Google Photos in a seamless manner. Optimized bug fixes for improved performance.

Say hello to VNTG app! A walk through the history of photography! Inspired by the most iconic instant cameras of all time with VNTG app you ll feel the nostalgia and get your best vintage photos. Select your desired VNTG Camera take or import as many photos as desired and transform them simultaneously in a single click! Share your memorable moments with family and friends! And with VNTG Print Service get your prints home! It is ideal for travel memories birthdays love gifts or any other special occasions. We have also improved the interface and user experience making it even easier and more comfortable to use. Enjoy VNTG!

Welcome to our new and improved InstaLab Editor! As promised! : Now you can create your Instant Photos more real than ever and inspired by the most iconic instant cameras of all time. It s easy fast and there s a whole bunch of possibilities! Select a photographic Style Classic Landscape Portrait Round Negative etc choose your preferred Filter B W Bright Chocolate Duotone Infrared Matte Monochrome Pastel Sepia etc and add a cool Effect Light Leaks Paper effect Bokeh Dust Old etc . You will also find many new Textures and Fonts for your texts old modern and much more realistic. We will continue adding new and exclusive content for special holidays occasions and moments. Create unique and much more personalized Instant Photos!
